      <title>由于美国数据阻碍降息押注，欧洲股市回吐涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-23/tech-stocks-lead-gains-in-europe-as-nvidia-results-boost-chips</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于通胀上升，美国商业活动加速，这可能会阻碍美联储降息，欧洲股市失去动力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-23/tech-stocks-lead-gains-in-europe-as-nvidia-results-boost-chips</guid>
